jasima.core.statistics

类 TimeWeightedSummaryStat

  • java.lang.Object
    • jasima.core.statistics.SummaryStat
      • jasima.core.statistics.TimeWeightedSummaryStat
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class TimeWeightedSummaryStat
extends SummaryStat
    A SummaryStat which weights values according to the time. As result statistics the values returned by SummaryStat.mean(), SummaryStat.min(), and SummaryStat.max() have defined values.
    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt

      • value

        public TimeWeightedSummaryStat value(double value,
                                     double time)
        Adds a new value, weighted by the difference between time and lastTime(). time is then saved for the next invocation of this method.
        覆盖:
        value 在类中 SummaryStat
        参数:
        value - Value of some state variable from the point in time given as the second parameter.
        time - The point in time from which the current value is value
        返回:
        this to allow easy chaining of calls.
